Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,++++++++
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们这么拼命的打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹们的身体会垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是神父的命令么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确保得到WitchBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我选择一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他应该已经对WitchBlade不感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说神父已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行部门在隐瞒真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神父亲口和我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅木
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 浅木小姐 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助神父把想要得到的东西拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是这个庞大的组织 还是预算
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在我掌控之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到一个玩偶而大吵大闹的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 只要把它弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有你的事了
